<div class="areaHeader" >Online Inventory Report & Ordering</div>

<p style="padding-bottom:20px;">Inventory updates daily at <strong>5 p.m. PST.</strong> Use the Shortcuts located at the bottom of the page to get to the product faster. Out of stock items/sizes are greyed out. You may call us to verify stock count if it is below 5. Call us at 1-800-468-5191 Mon - Fri 8 a.m - 4 p.m. PST. Review your order detail in the "Order Review" box to your right. <strong>Press the "Continue" button</strong> at the bottom of the page to continue. A window will open and you can submit the order after you fill out your information. <br />
<br />
<span class="style1">You will receive an "Order Received" email after submitting the order. If you don't see it, check your spam folder and add noreply@alegriashoes.com to your address book. </span><br />
<br />
<span class="style1">If you order contains more than 30 skus, please create multiple orders (each order with < 30 skus) and submit them separately.</span><br />
<br />

Our sales rep will contact you to follow up on your order. If you need technical assistance, please email <a href="mailto:wilson@peppergate.com">support</a>.